  <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Cryptogenic organizing pneumonia is inflammation and scarring of the small airways and air sacs of the lungs. The exact cause is not understood, but an autoimmune response is suspected.</rdfs:comment>
