  <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Dermatomyositis is an autoimmune disease that causes symptoms in the skin and muscles.  The symptoms are variable from patient to patient.   Affected populations can be grouped into juvenile and adult dermatomyositis.  The juvenile group tends to have gastrointestinal issues as well.</rdfs:comment>
  <ARI_DefSource rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Reeder 2010; https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2886726/</ARI_DefSource>
  <evidenceQuality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Antibody</evidenceQuality>
