  <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Enthesitis-related arthritis is diagnosed when rheumatoid arthritis affects the entheses, the connective tissue between a tendon or ligament and a bone.  Enthesitis affects about 15% of patients with juvenile arthritis.</rdfs:comment>
