  <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Idiopathic pulmonary fibrosis is a scarring of the lungs. It is suspected that the scarring is due to an autoinflammatory or autoimmune response.  However, there are other causes, and only a fraction of patients with IPF suffer from an autoimmune form of the disease.</rdfs:comment>
