  <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Damage caused by the autoimmune system to the myelin (covering surrounding nerves) of the optical nerves and spine, which affects vision and may also result in other neurological symptoms.</rdfs:comment>
