  <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Sicca syndrome is marked by dry mouth and dry eyes. If these symptoms are caused by an autoimmune process, it is called Sjogren's disease. See &lt;a href="/Disease_Profile/Sj%C3%B6grens-disease.aspx"&gt;Sjögrens disease for more information.</rdfs:comment>
