  <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Inflammation of the spinal cord with neurological effects that go in a transverse (horizontal or bandlike) manner across the body, as opposed to going up or down the spinal cord.</rdfs:comment>
